## Phase2 â€” Orientation Infrastructure âś…

**Goal:** Enable flexible rotation without breaking the game loop.

### Done

- [x] `app.json` `"orientation"` â†’ `"default"`
- [x] Android: removed static `screenOrientation="landscape"`
- [x] `src/hooks/useOrientation.ts`
